text: Amazing customer service, great and cozy space. Nice hospitality.

I had the croissant chicken ham with melted cheese and basque burnt cheesecake for dessert. The food was amazing and a friendly service. Brought the ondeh ondeh cake for takeaway and absolutely loved it!
Cosy atmosphere and amazing service.The owner is so kind! The crispy beef wrap was amazing.Glad to finally have halal food so much nearer to the office!
Arrived at 2.30pm on Friday. Place was empty and seems permanently closed
Great atmosphere, great coffee. If you're nearby, do drop by. They have coffee, cakes and bakes.
